      • getGlobalXmiResourceURI

        public static org.eclipse.emf.common.util.URI getGlobalXmiResourceURI(XmiModelUtilRunningOptionEnum optionEnum,
                                                      java.lang.String bundleName)
                                                               throws IncQueryException
        Returns the URI for global XMI Model located at path queries/globalEiqModel.xmi in the given bundle/project. First tries to resolve the path with platformResource (in workspace), if not found, uses the platformPluginURI (in bundles), if not found in here either, throws IncQueryException.
        Parameters:
        bundleName - workspace project name or platform bundle name.
        optionEnum - the option whether to use Resource or Plugin or both type of URIs
        Returns:
        the EMF resource URI pointing to the XMI store of generated pattern
        Throws:
        IncQueryException - when the global XMI model is not found in bundle/project
